# Generated dictionary data chunks — large files, not committed.
# Regenerate locally with: python3 tools/build-dict.py
#
# v2 structure:
#   src/data/{dir}/index/*.json  — slim chunks for seeding (only h.json committed as sample)
#   src/data/{dir}/data/*.json   — full chunks for lazy loading (all ignored)

# Ignore all data/ subdirectories (full chunks, ~45MB per direction)
